N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 49.13 - Application of part

State Regulations
(a) This Part shall
become effective forthwith. (b) Whenever the word licensee is used herein, it shall mean and include an
individual licensee, each member of a partnership licensee, each officer, director and substantial stockholder of a corporate licensee, and any agent, employee or servant of such licensee. Notes
